{"tid":865404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20潛水員搜救失蹤蛙人","createTime":"2018-10-17T04:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T06:54:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"576d3ef8d42f7b2419b526156ab26e8ee4fc8f4b","tid":865404,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181017/20523863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F20523863&d=5g6g7%2BRVn3vTr1Cz%2FSVwEl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0e6be1d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F20523863&h=54f0184b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181017/20523863</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月17日 <br />\n<br />\n20潛水員搜救失蹤蛙人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181017/large/a0706a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181017%2Flarge%2Fa0706a.gif&h=bcdeeea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港職業潛水協會成員昨晨在石鼓洲協助搜索失蹤潛水員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】水警及消防昨日繼續在石鼓洲對開海面，搜尋前日在海底進行潛水工作時失蹤的53歲蔡姓潛水員，但至晚上仍無任何發現。為盡快搜救該潛水員，約20名香港職業潛水協會的成員，昨晨亦加入搜救行列。他們於早上10時半乘船抵達出事海面後，隨即帶同潛水設備分批落水，惟並無發現。<br />\n<br />\n意外現場在石鼓洲對開30米海面，為「綜合廢物管理設施第一期」焚化爐工程所在位置。<br />\n<br />\n事發於前早8時許，蔡與兩名同事乘坐一艘小艇到上址，搶修被颱風山竹吹至鬆脫的浮標，蔡繫上聯絡繩後獨自潛落水底，其間，船家疑因小艇漂近岸邊，突然開動引擎，車葉割斷聯絡繩，蔡所穿的潛水裝備亦浮上水面，其同事知不妙即落水搜索，但蔡已失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n大批救援人員接報到場進行海空搜索，於當日早上11時許，消防蛙人在現場海域撈獲一截右手前臂殘肢，不排除屬於蔡姓失蹤潛水員，有待化驗確定。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查後，以涉嫌危害他人海上安全拘捕58歲姓梁船家，由水警總區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃祺文  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n搭的士爭執　英漢扑車窗傷女司機<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n昨晚六合彩開獎結果"},{"pid":"043896e7578a2f7e1773440e91bc24fc07c20e58","tid":865404,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"船家疑因小艇漂近岸邊，突然開動引擎，車葉割斷聯絡繩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022a87944ba1d4e4794b1b272092ef7ceca47e27","tid":865404,"uid":55384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 告謀殺啦"},{"pid":"67f444e33b89a817db293702cf20f1244696895f","tid":865404,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"043896e7578a2f7e1773440e91bc24fc07c20e58","tid":865404,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"船家疑因小艇漂近岸邊，突然開動引擎，車葉割斷聯絡繩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b70089820c0614cca18a0def8514a6907274b60","tid":865404,"uid":66395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67f444e33b89a817db293702cf20f1244696895f","tid":865404,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"043896e7578a2f7e1773440e91bc24fc07c20e58","tid":865404,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"船家疑因小艇漂近岸邊，突然開動引擎，車葉割斷聯絡繩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:40:15.000Z","msg":"會唔會割斷埋第二D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb574484d2539d0809a055ae242f92331c29c92","tid":865404,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:54:28.000Z","msg":"割斷線<br />\n潛水裝備浮上水面<br />\n搵到斷臂<br />\n好多疑點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}